stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE

    IDLE --> PLANNING: goal received
    PLANNING --> EXECUTING: path found
    PLANNING --> ABORTED: planning failed
    PLANNING --> PREEMPTED: newer goal
    PLANNING --> CANCELED: cancel request

    EXECUTING --> SUCCEEDED: goal tolerance reached
    EXECUTING --> REPLANNING: path entered replan margin
    EXECUTING --> WAITING_CLEARANCE: current state clearance violated
    EXECUTING --> PREEMPTED: newer goal
    EXECUTING --> CANCELED: cancel request
    EXECUTING --> ABORTED: timeout or unrecoverable failure

    WAITING_CLEARANCE --> REPLANNING: recoverable window found
    WAITING_CLEARANCE --> ABORTED: recovery timeout or no valid path
    WAITING_CLEARANCE --> PREEMPTED: newer goal
    WAITING_CLEARANCE --> CANCELED: cancel request

    REPLANNING --> EXECUTING: new path published
    REPLANNING --> ABORTED: replanning failed
    REPLANNING --> PREEMPTED: newer goal
    REPLANNING --> CANCELED: cancel request
